summary: Adds a mage called Thranduin who can be found in the Dragonsreach to skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
Thranduin is a level 20 high elf wizard who is training as Farengars apprentice. He aspires to become an expert mage, and is looking to go on an adventure to better practice his skills. 

He can be found in the Dragonsreach in whiterun. Please like and leave comments if you enjoy this mod! 

Bugs/Issues: 
None. 

Campatible/Incompatible: 
Must be loaded after Ultimate follower overhaul.
author: DireWolf12345
